  "2138090": {
    "name": "玛莉的炼金工房 Remake ～萨尔布鲁克的炼金术士～",
    "steam_appid": 2138090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "“炼金工房”系列的原点在25周年纪念之际完全重制！<br>以从学院顺利毕业为目标，炼金术与冒险同在，能做的事情数不胜数。<br>在炼金工房中悠悠度日，享受闲适生活的RPG！<br><br><strong>【故事】</strong><br>玛丽是一名就学于王立魔法学校（通称：学院）的吊车尾学生，<br>某天，她从老师那里得到一间为通过毕业考试而准备的炼金术工房。<br><br>毕业考试的题目是，做出获得老师肯首的道具。<br><br>为此，玛莉必须提高炼金术的技术、收集调合材料，还要赚取雇佣冒险者、购买参考书和道具的资金……调合、战斗、委托，能做的事情不胜枚举！<br><br>要从哪里开始全凭玩家决定！自在随心游玩，设法从学院顺利毕业吧。<br><br><strong>【本作的亮点】</strong><br><strong>■全新画面！用现代技术描绘出更加生动活泼的玛莉等人！</strong><br>本作使用了全新的角色立绘、事件插图，并且加载了2D动画。<br>此外，登场人物及场景也实现3D模型化。在移动或探索等行动中，可爱的迷你角色们会来回走动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/0385b73954450d521325f93173aaf237.poster.avif?t=1760597004\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/0385b73954450d521325f93173aaf237.webm?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/0385b73954450d521325f93173aaf237.mp4?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■迎合当今潮流，更易上手游玩的“炼金工房”系列之原点</strong><br>本作不仅保留原版简洁且高度自由的游玩感，还充实了教学与各种新元素的引导。<br>此外，城镇内的移动或采集等方式也修改为符合当今玩家的喜好，让玩家在游玩上更加轻松自如。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/eb1baec6b6da7314e44e4583b940c981.poster.avif?t=1760597004\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/eb1baec6b6da7314e44e4583b940c981.webm?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/eb1baec6b6da7314e44e4583b940c981.mp4?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■追加多项丰富游戏体验的新要素！</strong><br>本作追加诸多令人惊喜的全新要素，不仅是原版玩家，初次游玩“炼金工房”系列的新玩家也能乐在其中。<br>比如能悠闲游玩的“无限期模式”、与追加角色们的交流事件、有着华丽演出的必杀技等，帮助玩家进一步畅游充实精彩的游戏世界！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/1513893a50863d79cc40831c7d6c4f3e.poster.avif?t=1760597004\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/1513893a50863d79cc40831c7d6c4f3e.webm?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138090/extras/1513893a50863d79cc40831c7d6c4f3e.mp4?t=1760597004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
